commit.message: Updated the ChangeLog for the version requiremnt changes.
Switch to using `require_relative` to improve load-times (closes #15).
Added ruby-3.3 to the CI matrix.
Added ruby-3.2 to the CI matrix.
Quote ruby version numbers to prevent them from being parsed as floats.
Drop ruby-2.x from the CI matrix.
Use GitHub Flavored Markdown syntax highlighting.
Remove my email from the README.
Run CI on all branches and PRs.
